description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20 Minute Fat Burning Workout | High Intensity Interval Training' from the channel Global Cycling Network.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Join us for another indoor cycling training session, this 20 minute workout is one of the best ways to burn fat and get fit fast. The high intensity interval session will hurt so make sure you've got plenty of water and a towel for your hard earned sweat!
